# 5. step_dummy                        → Encode nominal
# 6. step_smote/rose (opsional)        → Balancing (SETELAH dummy!)
# 7. step_normalize                    → Normalisasi (WAJIB untuk KNN/SVM/NN)
# 8. step_spatialsign (opsional)       → Tangani outlier SETELAH normalisasi
# 9. step_pca (opsional)               → Reduksi dimensi SETELAH normalisasi
# 10. step_corr                        → Hapus multikolinearitas
# 11. step_nzv                         → Hapus zero-variance
# ============================================================================
```

